  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "ClearAll[M1, M2, M3, F1, F2]\r\nreplacebc = {\r\n(I*q2*(-(p*t2)/m+x))/hbar -> q2*M1,\r\n-(I*q2*(-(p*t2)/m+x))/hbar -> -q2*M1,\r\n(-p*(t1+t2)/m+x + (q2*t1)/(2*m)) -> (F1+q2*M2),\r\n(-p*(t1+t2)/m+x + (q2*t1)/(2*m))^2 -> (F1+q2*M2)^2,\r\n(-1/2*(p - q2/2)/\\[Sigma]p^2 - q/\\[Sigma]q^2) -> (M3*q2-F2),\r\n(-1/2*(p - q2/2)/\\[Sigma]p^2 - q/\\[Sigma]q^2)^2 -> (M3*q2-F2)^2\r\n};\r\nres6 = res5 /. replacebc\r\nInputForm[res6]",
